French professional basketball player with NBA's San Antonio Spurs, Tony Parker helped the Spurs win three NBA Championships in 2003, 2005 and 2007.

The 6' 1" starting point guard was selected as an NBA All-Star twice (2006; 2007) and was the 2007 NBA Finals MVP.

He is also branching out into music and plans to release a French hip-hop album.

